source.name: Monthly hydropower generation data by facility, US Bureau of Reclamation.
source.description: The Bureau of Reclamation provides monthly net hydropower generation data on a per facility basis for the past 10 years.  The data will be updated monthly with a quarterly delay to allow for data verification; i.e., October generation data would be available the following January.
